#OOPS

Abstraction - Just what is visible to the user
Inheritance - inheriting the features from parent class to the child class
Polymorphism - To display a message in more than one form.
eg:- UMS that have both different interface for both students and faculty
    -Runtime Polymorphism (method Overriding - )
    -Compile time Polymorphism (Method Overloading- same name different parameters)
Encapsulation - Binding the data into a single unit


#ENCAPSULATION
Getter $ Setter should be public
Data Members & Methods will be Private